{
  "stem": "10835.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But what we saw going out into the streets-- by the way, I forgot to mention that we were required to wear armbands.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At that time, it was a blue-- a white armband with a blue Star of David.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was about three inches wide.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were required to wear it I think on my left arm if I'm not mistaken.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And going out into the street, we had more or less enough freedom during the day.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we-- going out into the street, we could see SS people, I would call it, escorting at prisoners who were wearing these pajama-type uniforms.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they would take them out to clean the streets, sweep the streets, march them to do menial labor, from time to time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't see them all the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But later, little by little, we saw more, more and more of those.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In fact, comes into my memory a certain SS man who distinguished himself by being very tall.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was so tall that-- unusually tall.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was very-- how shall I say?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He used to yell at the prisoners.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he would poke them with the butt of the rifle for nothing at all.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And somehow, still being young, we didn't-- we didn't know what time will bring.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then 1941-- Well, [INAUDIBLE] during that time, you were still with your family?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were all together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were able to get food once we had money.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We would go out and buy, of course, with ration cards, you know?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the food was-- of course, we didn't have-- there wasn't everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But there were vegetables.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There were vegetables.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were bread.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was some meat.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
